{"tid":1132319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"把韓粉當暴民？花蓮警防暴演練    聚眾高舉凍蒜(當選)標語   怒喊「我要大發財！」惹議","createTime":"2019-04-30T08:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T11:14:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b22ab4b4ef751e92d309797cdd33c327e0d3f472","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"把韓粉當暴民？花蓮警鎮暴演練喊「發大財」惹議<br />\n<br />\n2019/04/30<br />\n<br />\n明年1月總統大選在即，花蓮縣警察局舉辦機動保安警力演練，模擬暴民的警察不斷大喊「我要發財、我要發財！」激動衝撞防暴部隊，但口號引來韓粉憤怒，質疑警方先入為主把韓粉當成暴民，警方急忙滅火，今日正式檢測聽不到「發大財」兩字，以免惹議。<br />\n<br />\n明年1月11日總統、立委選舉將屆，警政署為提升警方處理聚眾陳抗應變能力，30日上午在花蓮縣警局前廣場舉辦演練，縣警局前一天先行預演，模擬選後有民眾「輸不起」質疑選舉不公，聚眾高舉凍蒜標語，怒喊「我要發財！」和警力爆發推擠衝突。<br />\n<br />\n警方在指揮官下令下，吹哨以優勢警力展開鎮暴驅離，演練獲得縣警局高層高度肯定，不過員警模擬暴民演練口號，惹怒花蓮的韓粉，一旁議會職員聽到後也覺得不妥，有支持者認為有「被嘲諷」的感覺，警方察覺民怨並得知有媒體前來拍攝，收斂不再喊「發財」口號。<br />\n<br />\n今日正式演練，花蓮警方模擬兩方候選人支持群眾叫囂對峙等各種狀況，鎮暴警力到場壓制化解一觸及發的衝突場面，演練逼真，至於韓粉「發大財」口號也不再出現；對此，縣警局澄清，腳本是由保安隊模擬，當時可能是員警即興亂喊，沒有特別針對韓粉或特定對象演練暴動。<br />\n<br />\n到場檢閱的警政委員陳永利說，針對防制總統及立委大選網路聚眾滋事，警政署已經研擬一套作業流程，由警政署保安組統合警力調配因應，這次防暴演練特別加入網路聚眾示威遊行防暴演練，務求做好大選相關維安工作，也給予演練警方高度肯定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190430002405-260402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190430002405-260402&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1a0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=719c99f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190430002405-260402</a>"},{"pid":"662f52775bc165e6500abf427701abeca2e38969","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee28ba8884ad71efb824b0a7977bda108dfe38c0","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"標題打錯<br />\n....喊「我要<span style=\"color: red;\">發大財</span>」惹議"},{"pid":"c1f3b4349870627984e321a8647ae3b4acddaf9e","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"&quot;我要發財&quot;韓粉也要對號入座<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17107bed5303c2e1ea7443d712a0007550b3dc73","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58d6df0c7351e81035e20681e8d685e1bd33c8a","tid":1132319,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>這次防暴演練特別加入網絡聚眾示威遊行防暴演練</blockquote><br />\n鍵盤勇士有可能上街咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c740ced03fcc1a66d350131cf17fba87a4aa6b","tid":1132319,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb53e67145e0c69ab009c02d790aab1e9ca6d4","tid":1132319,"uid":26601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e54cc9f8279e9a1d13db86f708dd9e5a171a18a","tid":1132319,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />占中暴民"},{"pid":"fed29e667739f81f991c6d82e4e587ba804ddc74","tid":1132319,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:13:36.000Z","msg":"花蓮好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce202eca1a7cc891fee6a3eed1d1b448b981d3d","tid":1132319,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"韓總有支共支持  <br />\n點可能會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"